oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kenneth Hinson with Type
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fairs; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Hinson, Kenneth;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white half-length portrait of Kenneth Hinson standing in front of a table of type and looking at a group of papers being shown to him by possibly Jim Sherraden. The photo might have been taken at an outdoor fair.
